{
  "audio_path": "/Users/leohuang/podsearch/data/raw_audio/The_Indicator_from_Planet_Money/8b94cf8a-b9c6-405b-b755-ff8a8da4ee05.mp3",
  "language": "en",
  "duration": 528.90125,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.62,
      "end": 2.62,
      "text": " And P.R."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.62,
      "end": 14.69,
      "text": " Here's how you'll equine usually introduce"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.69,
      "end": 16.69,
      "text": " to themselves in social situations."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.69,
      "end": 19.19,
      "text": " Just do you should say I work at Google."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.19,
      "end": 21.19,
      "text": " And if they ask me more questions, I don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 21.19,
      "end": 24.19,
      "text": " I kind of feel weird about it saying what I do."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.19,
      "end": 26.19,
      "text": " And if they really, like, trust me on, like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.19,
      "end": 27.19,
      "text": " I don't know, what is your title?"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.19,
      "end": 29.69,
      "text": " It's like, well, I'm, like, VP there."
    },
    {
      "start": 29.69,
      "end": 32.69,
      "text": " Yeah, I mean, Yoong says he's a pretty introverted guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.69,
      "end": 35.69,
      "text": " And that actually might be surprising for people who know him"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.69,
      "end": 38.19,
      "text": " from something he did back in 2006."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.19,
      "end": 40.19,
      "text": " It comes down to one vote left."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.19,
      "end": 44.76,
      "text": " The winner of Survivor Cook Islands."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.76,
      "end": 48.3,
      "text": " That's right."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.3,
      "end": 52.3,
      "text": " Yoong Kwan is one of 47 people on the planet"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.3,
      "end": 56.3,
      "text": " who have won the legendary reality TV show Survivor."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.3,
      "end": 59.3,
      "text": " This is legendary economics podcast,"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.3,
      "end": 61.3,
      "text": " the indicator from Planet Money."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.3,
      "end": 62.3,
      "text": " I'm Will and Wong."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.3,
      "end": 63.3,
      "text": " And I'm Diane Boards."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.3,
      "end": 65.3,
      "text": " Survivor is roughly halfway through."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.3,
      "end": 67.3,
      "text": " It's 50th season."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.3,
      "end": 70.3,
      "text": " And one way to look at this long running reality TV series"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.3,
      "end": 73.3,
      "text": " is as a microcosm of the workplace."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.3,
      "end": 75.3,
      "text": " Sometimes there's collaboration"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.3,
      "end": 77.3,
      "text": " and sometimes there's scheming."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.3,
      "end": 80.3,
      "text": " Yes, there are complex social dynamics at play"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.3,
      "end": 82.3,
      "text": " and plenty of game theory."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.3,
      "end": 84.3,
      "text": " So to do on the show,"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.3,
      "end": 86.3,
      "text": " three previous Survivor winners tell us"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.3,
      "end": 88.3,
      "text": " about the careers before the show."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.3,
      "end": 90.3,
      "text": " And the skills they learned on the job"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.3,
      "end": 93.3,
      "text": " that help them come out on top."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.3,
      "end": 99.08,
      "text": " Every story from shortwave and pure science podcast"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.08,
      "end": 101.08,
      "text": " starts with a question."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.08,
      "end": 103.08,
      "text": " Like, why do we have nightmares?"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.08,
      "end": 106.08,
      "text": " How does AI affect my energy bill?"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.08,
      "end": 107.08,
      "text": " At NPR,"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.08,
      "end": 110.08,
      "text": " we are here for your right to be curious"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.08,
      "end": 112.08,
      "text": " about the world around you."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.08,
      "end": 114.08,
      "text": " Follow shortwave wherever you get your podcast"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.08,
      "end": 116.08,
      "text": " because the more you ask,"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.08,
      "end": 118.08,
      "text": " the more interesting the world gets."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.08,
      "end": 122.16,
      "text": " If you've never seen Survivor before,"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.16,
      "end": 124.16,
      "text": " here's the basic premise."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.16,
      "end": 126.16,
      "text": " You take about 20 strangers"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.16,
      "end": 128.16,
      "text": " and maroon them on an island."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.16,
      "end": 130.16,
      "text": " They have to work together for food,"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.16,
      "end": 131.16,
      "text": " water and shelter."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.16,
      "end": 133.16,
      "text": " They're competing in physical challenges"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.16,
      "end": 135.16,
      "text": " and they're recorded 24-7"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.16,
      "end": 138.16,
      "text": " and edited for Maximum TV drama."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.16,
      "end": 139.16,
      "text": " During the season,"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.16,
      "end": 141.16,
      "text": " the contestants start voting each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.16,
      "end": 142.16,
      "text": " off the island"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.16,
      "end": 145.16,
      "text": " and then when there are only a couple of people left,"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.16,
      "end": 146.16,
      "text": " all of the eliminated contestants"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.16,
      "end": 148.16,
      "text": " vote on the winner."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.16,
      "end": 150.16,
      "text": " The prize is $1 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.16,
      "end": 152.16,
      "text": " and there's lying involved"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.16,
      "end": 153.16,
      "text": " manipulation,"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.16,
      "end": 155.16,
      "text": " plenty of social engineering."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.16,
      "end": 157.16,
      "text": " And for you, at least,"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.16,
      "end": 158.16,
      "text": " some game theory."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.16,
      "end": 160.16,
      "text": " You know, strategy and trying to maximize results."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.16,
      "end": 163.16,
      "text": " One thing I used is a strategy called TIT for Cat."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.16,
      "end": 165.16,
      "text": " You start off being nice"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.16,
      "end": 166.16,
      "text": " and now as long as the other person's"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.16,
      "end": 168.16,
      "text": " nice, you keep being nice."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.16,
      "end": 170.16,
      "text": " But you don't take crap"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.16,
      "end": 172.16,
      "text": " like if the other person"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.16,
      "end": 173.16,
      "text": " tries to like hurt you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.16,
      "end": 174.16,
      "text": " you retaliate."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.16,
      "end": 175.16,
      "text": " But if the other person"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.16,
      "end": 177.16,
      "text": " starts working with you again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.16,
      "end": 178.16,
      "text": " you don't whole-grudge"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.16,
      "end": 179.16,
      "text": " and start cooperating with them again."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.16,
      "end": 181.16,
      "text": " Before competing on Survivor,"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.16,
      "end": 183.16,
      "text": " you'll always a management consultant"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.16,
      "end": 184.16,
      "text": " at McKinsey."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.16,
      "end": 186.16,
      "text": " Other contestants have been cops,"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.16,
      "end": 188.16,
      "text": " firefighters, office workers, and surgeons."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.16,
      "end": 191.16,
      "text": " Kyle Frazier, the winner of Survivor 48,"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.16,
      "end": 193.16,
      "text": " was an attorney before the show,"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.16,
      "end": 196.16,
      "text": " and his legal training was useful on Survivor."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.16,
      "end": 198.16,
      "text": " He told us that in law school around five years ago,"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.16,
      "end": 200.16,
      "text": " he got to defend a client at trial,"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.16,
      "end": 203.16,
      "text": " which is rare for a law student to do."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.16,
      "end": 205.16,
      "text": " In his opening argument at that trial,"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.16,
      "end": 206.16,
      "text": " he just owned it."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.16,
      "end": 207.16,
      "text": " I'm a law student."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.16,
      "end": 209.16,
      "text": " I haven't even studied evidence yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.16,
      "end": 210.16,
      "text": " I didn't see that."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.16,
      "end": 212.16,
      "text": " But I may clear to them"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.16,
      "end": 214.16,
      "text": " that I care about this case,"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.16,
      "end": 215.16,
      "text": " and that I'm going to do my best"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.16,
      "end": 216.16,
      "text": " to advocate for my client."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.16,
      "end": 218.16,
      "text": " I think that we connected with the jury more"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.16,
      "end": 219.16,
      "text": " than the seasoned prosecutor"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.16,
      "end": 221.16,
      "text": " who had had probably 15, 20 years"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.16,
      "end": 222.16,
      "text": " and rebunked at that time."
    },
    {
      "start": 222.16,
      "end": 223.16,
      "text": " He was like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.16,
      "end": 224.16,
      "text": " Kyle had to present something"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.16,
      "end": 226.16,
      "text": " like a closing argument on Survivor."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.16,
      "end": 228.16,
      "text": " And remember he had to make his case"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.16,
      "end": 229.16,
      "text": " to everyone he had helped"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.16,
      "end": 231.16,
      "text": " and vote off earlier in the season."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.16,
      "end": 233.16,
      "text": " Kyle decided to use the same strategy."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.16,
      "end": 235.16,
      "text": " He came totally clean."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.16,
      "end": 237.16,
      "text": " And so I had to make clear"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.16,
      "end": 238.16,
      "text": " that I care about each and every one of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.16,
      "end": 240.16,
      "text": " that you saw exactly who I am as a person,"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.16,
      "end": 241.16,
      "text": " but at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.16,
      "end": 243.16,
      "text": " the allegiances that I have to my fiance"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.16,
      "end": 245.16,
      "text": " now wipe that home and my family"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.16,
      "end": 246.16,
      "text": " drop everything,"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.16,
      "end": 248.16,
      "text": " and I hope you can understand that."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.16,
      "end": 249.16,
      "text": " And that's my pitch."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.16,
      "end": 252.16,
      "text": " Survivor is a complex social game."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.16,
      "end": 254.16,
      "text": " Winning takes navigating"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.16,
      "end": 255.16,
      "text": " fragile interpersonal dynamics"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.16,
      "end": 257.16,
      "text": " and building trust with people"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.16,
      "end": 259.16,
      "text": " who have a million-dollar incentive"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.16,
      "end": 260.16,
      "text": " to lie to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.16,
      "end": 262.16,
      "text": " Savannah Louis worked as a TV station"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.16,
      "end": 264.16,
      "text": " reporter before winning last year"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.16,
      "end": 265.16,
      "text": " Survivor 49."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.16,
      "end": 267.16,
      "text": " She says the interpersonal skills"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.16,
      "end": 269.16,
      "text": " she honed during her career"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.16,
      "end": 270.16,
      "text": " came in handy on Survivor."
    },
    {
      "start": 270.16,
      "end": 272.16,
      "text": " I've been unintentionally training"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.16,
      "end": 274.16,
      "text": " for Survivor for the past decade"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.16,
      "end": 276.16,
      "text": " because of my work as a journalist."
    },
    {
      "start": 276.16,
      "end": 278.16,
      "text": " And so I thought that I could use"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.16,
      "end": 280.16,
      "text": " those people's skills"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.16,
      "end": 282.16,
      "text": " to get the right people to trust me."
    },
    {
      "start": 282.16,
      "end": 284.16,
      "text": " The right people."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.16,
      "end": 285.16,
      "text": " Because again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.16,
      "end": 287.16,
      "text": " much of Survivor involves lying."
    },
    {
      "start": 287.16,
      "end": 289.16,
      "text": " So the last thing you want to do"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.16,
      "end": 291.16,
      "text": " is think someone is her ally."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.16,
      "end": 292.16,
      "text": " When in fact, they're conspiring to"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.16,
      "end": 293.16,
      "text": " Ausju."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.16,
      "end": 295.16,
      "text": " Here's Savannah on an episode of Survivor"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.16,
      "end": 297.16,
      "text": " putting the screws on someone"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.16,
      "end": 298.16,
      "text": " she thought was planning"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.16,
      "end": 299.16,
      "text": " on voting her out."
    },
    {
      "start": 299.16,
      "end": 302.16,
      "text": " I know Christina wants me gone so bad."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.16,
      "end": 303.16,
      "text": " So I'll just be real."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.16,
      "end": 304.16,
      "text": " I'm someone who's very direct."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.16,
      "end": 306.16,
      "text": " If I want to know who you're voting for,"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.16,
      "end": 307.16,
      "text": " I'm going to ask you."
    },
    {
      "start": 307.16,
      "end": 308.16,
      "text": " Who are you voting for?"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.16,
      "end": 309.16,
      "text": " Who also are you considering?"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.16,
      "end": 310.16,
      "text": " Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 310.16,
      "end": 311.16,
      "text": " Who else are you considering?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.16,
      "end": 313.16,
      "text": " Savannah told us that her"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.16,
      "end": 315.16,
      "text": " pointy question came right from her report"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.16,
      "end": 316.16,
      "text": " is toolkit."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.16,
      "end": 317.16,
      "text": " The one of the things that I learned"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.16,
      "end": 318.16,
      "text": " as a journalist is to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.16,
      "end": 319.16,
      "text": " very direct with people"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.16,
      "end": 321.16,
      "text": " when you're questioning them."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.16,
      "end": 322.16,
      "text": " She was so flustered"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.16,
      "end": 323.16,
      "text": " and I could tell in that moment"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.16,
      "end": 325.16,
      "text": " she's obviously going against me"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.16,
      "end": 326.16,
      "text": " or my allies."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.16,
      "end": 328.16,
      "text": " She's someone who I can't trust."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.16,
      "end": 329.16,
      "text": " So if now heard from Survivor winners"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.16,
      "end": 331.16,
      "text": " who were a management consultant"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.16,
      "end": 333.16,
      "text": " and attorney and a TV reporter,"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.16,
      "end": 335.16,
      "text": " all professions at hinge"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.16,
      "end": 336.16,
      "text": " on direct communication"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.16,
      "end": 337.16,
      "text": " and relationship building."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.16,
      "end": 339.16,
      "text": " Now, one of the more common"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.16,
      "end": 340.16,
      "text": " professions amongst Survivor winners"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.16,
      "end": 342.16,
      "text": " is protective services."
    },
    {
      "start": 342.16,
      "end": 343.16,
      "text": " That's according to an analysis"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.16,
      "end": 345.16,
      "text": " from the Bureau of Labor Statistics."
    },
    {
      "start": 345.16,
      "end": 346.16,
      "text": " Protective services"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.16,
      "end": 348.16,
      "text": " includes cops, firefighters"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.16,
      "end": 350.16,
      "text": " and security guards."
    },
    {
      "start": 350.16,
      "end": 351.16,
      "text": " And in fact,"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.16,
      "end": 352.16,
      "text": " one of the two people"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.16,
      "end": 353.16,
      "text": " who have won Survivor twice"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.16,
      "end": 355.16,
      "text": " came from this background."
    },
    {
      "start": 355.16,
      "end": 357.16,
      "text": " So this seems pretty intuitive."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.16,
      "end": 358.16,
      "text": " You know when you think about"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.16,
      "end": 359.16,
      "text": " the physical stamina"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.16,
      "end": 362.16,
      "text": " and survival skills needed to thrive"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.16,
      "end": 363.16,
      "text": " on a desert island?"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.16,
      "end": 365.16,
      "text": " Yeah, you don't learn those in podcasting."
    },
    {
      "start": 365.16,
      "end": 367.16,
      "text": " My mic lifting muscles are getting"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.16,
      "end": 368.16,
      "text": " pretty strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 368.16,
      "end": 369.16,
      "text": " Okay, Vadarian."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.16,
      "end": 370.16,
      "text": " Here's a plot twist."
    },
    {
      "start": 370.16,
      "end": 372.16,
      "text": " The BLS says the most common"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.16,
      "end": 374.16,
      "text": " profession for a Survivor winner"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.16,
      "end": 376.16,
      "text": " is actually management."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.16,
      "end": 378.16,
      "text": " You know, boardroom folks and executives,"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.16,
      "end": 379.16,
      "text": " CEOs and VPs."
    },
    {
      "start": 379.16,
      "end": 381.16,
      "text": " Plus people like Survivor 13"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.16,
      "end": 382.16,
      "text": " winner, Yul Kwan,"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.16,
      "end": 384.16,
      "text": " the former management consultant."
    },
    {
      "start": 384.16,
      "end": 387.16,
      "text": " Survivor is basically a show"
    },
    {
      "start": 387.16,
      "end": 390.16,
      "text": " about group dynamics and interpersonal relationships."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.16,
      "end": 392.16,
      "text": " It's about interacting with other people"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.16,
      "end": 394.16,
      "text": " and influencing them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.16,
      "end": 396.16,
      "text": " forging alliances and getting people"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.16,
      "end": 398.16,
      "text": " aligned behind a goal and a strategy"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.16,
      "end": 400.16,
      "text": " and executing against it."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.16,
      "end": 402.16,
      "text": " And that's basically what management is."
    },
    {
      "start": 402.16,
      "end": 404.16,
      "text": " And Yul told our producer,"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.16,
      "end": 405.16,
      "text": " that those management skills"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.16,
      "end": 408.16,
      "text": " were especially crucial in negotiations."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.16,
      "end": 409.16,
      "text": " Being able to understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.16,
      "end": 411.16,
      "text": " when people are responding"
    },
    {
      "start": 411.16,
      "end": 414.16,
      "text": " due to pressure as opposed to"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.16,
      "end": 415.16,
      "text": " how they would normally behave"
    },
    {
      "start": 415.16,
      "end": 416.16,
      "text": " if they were in character."
    },
    {
      "start": 416.16,
      "end": 418.16,
      "text": " And then using that in the"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.16,
      "end": 420.16,
      "text": " context of like negotiations"
    },
    {
      "start": 420.16,
      "end": 421.16,
      "text": " and just trying to make sure,"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.16,
      "end": 422.16,
      "text": " hey, you know what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.16,
      "end": 425.16,
      "text": " Let's lower the temperature in this room."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.16,
      "end": 426.16,
      "text": " Have there been any moments"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.16,
      "end": 428.16,
      "text": " in your professional life where you've been like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.16,
      "end": 430.16,
      "text": " oh man, if I were on Survivor,"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.16,
      "end": 431.16,
      "text": " here's how I would deal with this."
    },
    {
      "start": 431.16,
      "end": 432.16,
      "text": " You mean like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.16,
      "end": 434.16,
      "text": " if I could vote this person off the island,"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.16,
      "end": 435.16,
      "text": " I would,"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.16,
      "end": 436.16,
      "text": " ah, yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 436.16,
      "end": 440.16,
      "text": " If I could have a secret hidden vote"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.16,
      "end": 441.16,
      "text": " and just be like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.16,
      "end": 443.16,
      "text": " all right, this person is like gone"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.16,
      "end": 445.16,
      "text": " from ever having to deal with this person."
    },
    {
      "start": 445.16,
      "end": 447.16,
      "text": " Do you like his idea for a new kind of 360 review"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.16,
      "end": 448.16,
      "text": " Darian?"
    },
    {
      "start": 448.16,
      "end": 450.16,
      "text": " Yes, that does sound terrifying."
    },
    {
      "start": 450.16,
      "end": 453.16,
      "text": " I've got happy with my catch ups"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.16,
      "end": 454.16,
      "text": " from my manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 454.16,
      "end": 455.16,
      "text": " No, light the torches,"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.16,
      "end": 457.16,
      "text": " or holding a vote, Darian."
    },
    {
      "start": 457.16,
      "end": 458.16,
      "text": " And that's also why,"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.16,
      "end": 460.16,
      "text": " perhaps that Yul prefers"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.16,
      "end": 462.16,
      "text": " most of the time, they're real world."
    },
    {
      "start": 462.16,
      "end": 464.16,
      "text": " I'm so glad the world doesn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.16,
      "end": 465.16,
      "text": " work like this."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.16,
      "end": 467.16,
      "text": " I'm so glad the world is one"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.16,
      "end": 468.16,
      "text": " where, you know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.16,
      "end": 471.16,
      "text": " people fundamentally like"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.16,
      "end": 472.16,
      "text": " cooperate with one or one"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.16,
      "end": 473.16,
      "text": " to help one another."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.16,
      "end": 474.16,
      "text": " They're giving each other the better"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.16,
      "end": 475.16,
      "text": " for the doubt."
    },
    {
      "start": 475.16,
      "end": 476.16,
      "text": " You know,"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.16,
      "end": 477.16,
      "text": " and we actually get ahead"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.16,
      "end": 478.16,
      "text": " by working together."
    },
    {
      "start": 478.16,
      "end": 479.16,
      "text": " It's an inspiring message."
    },
    {
      "start": 479.16,
      "end": 480.16,
      "text": " Yeah, that's like our show,"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.16,
      "end": 482.16,
      "text": " maybe someone should do"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.16,
      "end": 484.16,
      "text": " a reality show about our team."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.16,
      "end": 485.16,
      "text": " Yeah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.16,
      "end": 486.16,
      "text": " indicator island,"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.16,
      "end": 488.16,
      "text": " you're on with two microphones"
    },
    {
      "start": 488.16,
      "end": 489.16,
      "text": " and the truth."
    },
    {
      "start": 489.16,
      "end": 491.16,
      "text": " Hahaha."
    },
    {
      "start": 491.16,
      "end": 493.16,
      "text": " I'll start packing my tote bag."
    },
    {
      "start": 493.16,
      "end": 498.08,
      "text": " It's not too late to come see"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.08,
      "end": 500.08,
      "text": " planet money live on our book tour."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.08,
      "end": 502.08,
      "text": " We've still got a bunch of stops"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.08,
      "end": 503.08,
      "text": " to make including Portland,"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.08,
      "end": 506.08,
      "text": " Los Angeles, and Chicago."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.08,
      "end": 507.08,
      "text": " We're all be."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.08,
      "end": 509.08,
      "text": " Go to planetmoneybook.com"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.08,
      "end": 512.08,
      "text": " where tickets, details, and dates."
    },
    {
      "start": 512.08,
      "end": 514.08,
      "text": " This episode was produced"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.08,
      "end": 515.08,
      "text": " by Vito Emanuel,"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.08,
      "end": 516.08,
      "text": " an engineer by Quissy Lee."
    },
    {
      "start": 516.08,
      "end": 518.08,
      "text": " It was fact-checked by Sierra Huades,"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.08,
      "end": 519.08,
      "text": " an edited by Julia Richie."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.08,
      "end": 520.08,
      "text": " The editor of the show is"
    },
    {
      "start": 520.08,
      "end": 521.08,
      "text": " Kicking Cannon,"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.08,
      "end": 522.08,
      "text": " and the indicator is a"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.08,
      "end": 523.08,
      "text": " production of NPR."
    }
  ]
}